{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":3000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":17000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":27000,"text":"I am a papercutter."},{"time":30000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":32000,"text":"I cut stories."},{"time":35000,"text":"So my process is very straightforward."},{"time":38000,"text":"I take a piece of paper,"},{"time":40000,"text":"I visualize my story,"},{"time":43000,"text":"sometimes I sketch, sometimes I don't."},{"time":46000,"text":"And as my image"},{"time":48000,"text":"is already inside the paper,"},{"time":51000,"text":"I just have to remove"},{"time":53000,"text":"what's not from that story."},{"time":56000,"text":"So I didn't come to papercutting"},{"time":59000,"text":"in a straight line."},{"time":61000,"text":"In fact,"},{"time":63000,"text":"I see it more as a spiral."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65000,"text":"I was not born"},{"time":67000,"text":"with a blade in my hand."},{"time":70000,"text":"And I don't remember papercutting as a child."},{"time":73000,"text":"As a teenager,"},{"time":75000,"text":"I was sketching, drawing,"},{"time":77000,"text":"and I wanted to be an artist."},{"time":79000,"text":"But I was also a rebel."},{"time":83000,"text":"And I left everything"},{"time":85000,"text":"and went for a long series of odd jobs."},{"time":89000,"text":"So among them,"},{"time":91000,"text":"I have been a shepherdess,"},{"time":94000,"text":"a truck driver,"},{"time":96000,"text":"a factory worker,"},{"time":98000,"text":"a cleaning lady."},{"time":100000,"text":"I worked in tourism for one year"},{"time":102000,"text":"in Mexico,"},{"time":104000,"text":"one year in Egypt."},{"time":107000,"text":"I moved for two years"},{"time":109000,"text":"in Taiwan."},{"time":111000,"text":"And then I settled in New York"},{"time":113000,"text":"where I became a tour guide."},{"time":115000,"text":"And I still worked as a tour leader,"},{"time":118000,"text":"traveled back and forth"},{"time":120000,"text":"in China, Tibet and Central Asia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123000,"text":"So of course, it took time, and I was nearly 40,"},{"time":126000,"text":"and I decided it's time"},{"time":128000,"text":"to start as an artist."},{"time":132000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":137000,"text":"I chose papercutting"},{"time":139000,"text":"because paper is cheap,"},{"time":141000,"text":"it's light,"},{"time":143000,"text":"and you can use it"},{"time":145000,"text":"in a lot of different ways."},{"time":147000,"text":"And I chose the language of silhouette"},{"time":151000,"text":"because graphically it's very efficient."},{"time":154000,"text":"And it's also just getting to the essential of things."},{"time":160000,"text":"So the word \"silhouette\""},{"time":162000,"text":"comes from a minister of finance,"},{"time":165000,"text":"Etienne de Silhouette."},{"time":168000,"text":"And he slashed so many budgets"},{"time":172000,"text":"that people said they couldn't afford"},{"time":174000,"text":"paintings anymore,"},{"time":176000,"text":"and they needed to have their portrait"},{"time":178000,"text":"\"a la silhouette.\""},{"time":180000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":182000,"text":"So I made series of images, cuttings,"},{"time":188000,"text":"and I assembled them in portfolios."},{"time":193000,"text":"And people told me --"},{"time":195000,"text":"like these 36 views of the Empire State building --"},{"time":198000,"text":"they told me, \"You're making artist books.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":202000,"text":"So artist books have a lot of definitions."},{"time":205000,"text":"They come in a lot of different shapes."},{"time":208000,"text":"But to me,"},{"time":210000,"text":"they are fascinating objects"},{"time":212000,"text":"to visually narrate a story."},{"time":215000,"text":"They can be with words"},{"time":217000,"text":"or without words."},{"time":220000,"text":"And I have a passion"},{"time":222000,"text":"for images and for words."},{"time":225000,"text":"I love pun"},{"time":227000,"text":"and the relation to the unconscious."},{"time":230000,"text":"I love oddities of languages."},{"time":233000,"text":"And everywhere I lived, I learned the languages,"},{"time":235000,"text":"but never mastered them."},{"time":237000,"text":"So I'm always looking"},{"time":239000,"text":"for the false cognates"},{"time":241000,"text":"or identical words in different languages."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244000,"text":"So as you can guess, my mother tongue is French."},{"time":247000,"text":"And my daily language is English."},{"time":251000,"text":"So I did a series of work"},{"time":253000,"text":"where it was identical words"},{"time":256000,"text":"in French and in English."},{"time":259000,"text":"So one of these works"},{"time":261000,"text":"is the \"Spelling Spider.\""},{"time":263000,"text":"So the Spelling Spider"},{"time":265000,"text":"is a cousin of the spelling bee."},{"time":268000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":270000,"text":"But it's much more connected to the Web."},{"time":273000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":275000,"text":"And this spider"},{"time":277000,"text":"spins a bilingual alphabet."},{"time":280000,"text":"So you can read \"architecture active\""},{"time":284000,"text":"or \"active architecture.\""},{"time":287000,"text":"So this spider goes through the whole alphabet"},{"time":290000,"text":"with identical adjectives and substantives."},{"time":294000,"text":"So if you don't know one of these languages,"},{"time":297000,"text":"it's instant learning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301000,"text":"And one ancient form of the book"},{"time":304000,"text":"is scrolls."},{"time":306000,"text":"So scrolls are very convenient,"},{"time":309000,"text":"because you can create a large image"},{"time":312000,"text":"on a very small table."},{"time":316000,"text":"So the unexpected consequences of that"},{"time":320000,"text":"is that you only see one part of your image,"},{"time":325000,"text":"so it makes a very freestyle architecture."},{"time":329000,"text":"And I'm making all those kinds of windows."},{"time":333000,"text":"So it's to look beyond the surface."},{"time":336000,"text":"It's to have a look"},{"time":338000,"text":"at different worlds."},{"time":340000,"text":"And very often I've been an outsider."},{"time":342000,"text":"So I want to see how things work"},{"time":345000,"text":"and what's happening."},{"time":347000,"text":"So each window"},{"time":349000,"text":"is an image"},{"time":351000,"text":"and is a world"},{"time":353000,"text":"that I often revisit."},{"time":355000,"text":"And I revisit this world"},{"time":357000,"text":"thinking about the image"},{"time":359000,"text":"or cliché about what we want to do,"},{"time":362000,"text":"and what are the words, colloquialisms,"},{"time":364000,"text":"that we have with the expressions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367000,"text":"It's all if."},{"time":370000,"text":"So what if we were living in balloon houses?"},{"time":375000,"text":"It would make a very uplifting world."},{"time":379000,"text":"And we would leave a very low footprint on the planet."},{"time":384000,"text":"It would be so light."},{"time":387000,"text":"So sometimes I view from the inside,"},{"time":392000,"text":"like EgoCentriCity"},{"time":394000,"text":"and the inner circles."},{"time":397000,"text":"Sometimes it's a global view,"},{"time":400000,"text":"to see our common roots"},{"time":403000,"text":"and how we can use them to catch dreams."},{"time":407000,"text":"And we can use them also"},{"time":409000,"text":"as a safety net."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"And my inspirations"},{"time":414000,"text":"are very eclectic."},{"time":418000,"text":"I'm influenced by everything I read,"},{"time":421000,"text":"everything I see."},{"time":424000,"text":"I have some stories that are humorous,"},{"time":427000,"text":"like \"Dead Beats.\""},{"time":430000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":433000,"text":"Other ones are historical."},{"time":435000,"text":"Here it's \"CandyCity.\""},{"time":437000,"text":"It's a non-sugar-coated"},{"time":439000,"text":"history of sugar."},{"time":441000,"text":"It goes from slave trade"},{"time":444000,"text":"to over-consumption of sugar"},{"time":447000,"text":"with some sweet moments in between."},{"time":451000,"text":"And sometimes I have an emotional response to news,"},{"time":454000,"text":"such as the 2010 Haitian earthquake."},{"time":460000,"text":"Other times, it's not even my stories."},{"time":463000,"text":"People tell me their lives,"},{"time":465000,"text":"their memories, their aspirations,"},{"time":468000,"text":"and I create a mindscape."},{"time":471000,"text":"I channel their history"},{"time":474000,"text":"[so that] they have a place to go back"},{"time":477000,"text":"to look at their life and its possibilities."},{"time":481000,"text":"I call them Freudian cities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485000,"text":"I cannot speak for all my images,"},{"time":487000,"text":"so I'll just go through a few of my worlds"},{"time":491000,"text":"just with the title."},{"time":493000,"text":"\"ModiCity.\""},{"time":497000,"text":"\"ElectriCity.\""},{"time":502000,"text":"\"MAD Growth on Columbus Circle.\""},{"time":510000,"text":"\"ReefCity.\""},{"time":514000,"text":"\"A Web of Time.\""},{"time":520000,"text":"\"Chaos City.\""},{"time":525000,"text":"\"Daily Battles.\""},{"time":530000,"text":"\"FeliCity.\""},{"time":534000,"text":"\"Floating Islands.\""},{"time":538000,"text":"And at one point,"},{"time":540000,"text":"I had to do \"The Whole Nine Yards.\""},{"time":543000,"text":"So it's actually a papercut that's nine yards long."},{"time":546000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":548000,"text":"So in life and in papercutting,"},{"time":550000,"text":"everything is connected."},{"time":552000,"text":"One story leads to another."},{"time":555000,"text":"I was also interested"},{"time":557000,"text":"in the physicality of this format,"},{"time":559000,"text":"because you have to walk to see it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":562000,"text":"And parallel to my cutting"},{"time":564000,"text":"is my running."},{"time":566000,"text":"I started with small images,"},{"time":568000,"text":"I started with a few miles."},{"time":570000,"text":"Larger images, I started to run marathons."},{"time":573000,"text":"Then I went to run 50K, then 60K."},{"time":576000,"text":"Then I ran 50 miles -- ultramarathons."},{"time":581000,"text":"And I still feel I'm running,"},{"time":584000,"text":"it's just the training"},{"time":586000,"text":"to become a long-distance papercutter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":591000,"text":"And running gives me a lot of energy."},{"time":595000,"text":"Here is a three-week papercutting marathon"},{"time":598000,"text":"at the Museum of Arts and Design"},{"time":601000,"text":"in New York City."},{"time":603000,"text":"The result is \"Hells and Heavens.\""},{"time":607000,"text":"It's two panels 13 ft. high."},{"time":610000,"text":"They were installed in the museum on two floors,"},{"time":613000,"text":"but in fact, it's a continuous image."},{"time":615000,"text":"And I call it \"Hells and Heavens\""},{"time":618000,"text":"because it's daily hells and daily heavens."},{"time":622000,"text":"There is no border in between."},{"time":624000,"text":"Some people are born in hells,"},{"time":626000,"text":"and against all odds, they make it to heavens."},{"time":629000,"text":"Other people make the opposite trip."},{"time":631000,"text":"That's the border."},{"time":633000,"text":"You have sweatshops in hells."},{"time":635000,"text":"You have people renting their wings in the heavens."},{"time":638000,"text":"And then you have all those individual stories"},{"time":641000,"text":"where sometimes we even have the same action,"},{"time":645000,"text":"and the result puts you in hells or in heavens."},{"time":650000,"text":"So the whole \"Hells and Heavens\""},{"time":652000,"text":"is about free will"},{"time":655000,"text":"and determinism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":657000,"text":"And in papercutting,"},{"time":659000,"text":"you have the drawing as the structure itself."},{"time":663000,"text":"So you can take it off the wall."},{"time":667000,"text":"Here it's an artist book installation"},{"time":670000,"text":"called \"Identity Project.\""},{"time":673000,"text":"It's not autobiographical identities."},{"time":677000,"text":"They are more our social identities."},{"time":681000,"text":"And then you can just walk behind them"},{"time":683000,"text":"and try them on."},{"time":685000,"text":"So it's like the different layers"},{"time":687000,"text":"of what we are made of"},{"time":689000,"text":"and what we present to the world"},{"time":691000,"text":"as an identity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693000,"text":"That's another artist book project."},{"time":696000,"text":"In fact, in the picture, you have two of them."},{"time":700000,"text":"It's one I'm wearing"},{"time":702000,"text":"and one that's on exhibition"},{"time":704000,"text":"at the Center for Books Arts in New York City."},{"time":706000,"text":"Why do I call it a book?"},{"time":708000,"text":"It's called \"Fashion Statement,\""},{"time":710000,"text":"and there are quotes about fashion,"},{"time":712000,"text":"so you can read it,"},{"time":714000,"text":"and also,"},{"time":716000,"text":"because the definition of artist book"},{"time":719000,"text":"is very generous."},{"time":722000,"text":"So artist books, you take them off the wall."},{"time":724000,"text":"You take them for a walk."},{"time":726000,"text":"You can also install them as public art."},{"time":729000,"text":"Here it's in Scottsdale, Arizona,"},{"time":732000,"text":"and it's called \"Floating Memories.\""},{"time":735000,"text":"So it's regional memories,"},{"time":738000,"text":"and they are just randomly moved by the wind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":743000,"text":"I love public art."},{"time":745000,"text":"And I entered competitions"},{"time":748000,"text":"for a long time."},{"time":750000,"text":"After eight years of rejection,"},{"time":753000,"text":"I was thrilled to get my first commission"},{"time":756000,"text":"with the Percent for Art in New York City."},{"time":759000,"text":"It was for a merger station"},{"time":762000,"text":"for emergency workers and firemen."},{"time":765000,"text":"I made an artist book"},{"time":768000,"text":"that's in stainless steel"},{"time":770000,"text":"instead of paper."},{"time":772000,"text":"I called it \"Working in the Same Direction.\""},{"time":776000,"text":"But I added weathervanes on both sides"},{"time":778000,"text":"to show that they cover all directions."},{"time":782000,"text":"With public art,"},{"time":784000,"text":"I could also make cut glass."},{"time":787000,"text":"Here it's faceted glass in the Bronx."},{"time":790000,"text":"And each time I make public art,"},{"time":792000,"text":"I want something that's really relevant"},{"time":794000,"text":"to the place it's installed."},{"time":796000,"text":"So for the subway in New York,"},{"time":798000,"text":"I saw a correspondence"},{"time":801000,"text":"between riding the subway"},{"time":804000,"text":"and reading."},{"time":806000,"text":"It is travel in time, travel on time."},{"time":809000,"text":"And Bronx literature,"},{"time":811000,"text":"it's all about Bronx writers"},{"time":813000,"text":"and their stories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":817000,"text":"Another glass project"},{"time":819000,"text":"is in a public library"},{"time":821000,"text":"in San Jose, California."},{"time":824000,"text":"So I made a vegetable point of view"},{"time":827000,"text":"of the growth of San Jose."},{"time":829000,"text":"So I started in the center"},{"time":831000,"text":"with the acorn"},{"time":833000,"text":"for the Ohlone Indian civilization."},{"time":837000,"text":"Then I have the fruit from Europe"},{"time":839000,"text":"for the ranchers."},{"time":841000,"text":"And then the fruit of the world for Silicon Valley today."},{"time":844000,"text":"And it's still growing."},{"time":846000,"text":"So the technique, it's cut,"},{"time":849000,"text":"sandblasted, etched"},{"time":851000,"text":"and printed glass into architectural glass."},{"time":855000,"text":"And outside the library,"},{"time":857000,"text":"I wanted to make a place to cultivate your mind."},{"time":861000,"text":"I took library material"},{"time":864000,"text":"that had fruit in their title"},{"time":867000,"text":"and I used them to make an orchard walk"},{"time":870000,"text":"with these fruits of knowledge."},{"time":872000,"text":"I also planted the bibliotree."},{"time":875000,"text":"So it's a tree,"},{"time":877000,"text":"and in its trunk you have the roots of languages."},{"time":880000,"text":"And it's all about international writing systems."},{"time":884000,"text":"And on the branches"},{"time":886000,"text":"you have library material growing."},{"time":890000,"text":"You can also have function and form"},{"time":893000,"text":"with public art."},{"time":895000,"text":"So in Aurora, Colorado it's a bench."},{"time":897000,"text":"But you have a bonus with this bench."},{"time":900000,"text":"Because if you sit a long time in summer in shorts,"},{"time":903000,"text":"you will walk away"},{"time":905000,"text":"with temporary branding of"},{"time":908000,"text":"the story element on your thighs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":910000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":915000,"text":"Another functional work,"},{"time":917000,"text":"it's in the south side of Chicago"},{"time":919000,"text":"for a subway station."},{"time":921000,"text":"And it's called \"Seeds of the Future are Planted Today.\""},{"time":925000,"text":"It's a story about transformation"},{"time":928000,"text":"and connections."},{"time":930000,"text":"So it acts as a screen"},{"time":932000,"text":"to protect the rail and the commuter,"},{"time":935000,"text":"and not to have objects falling on the rails."},{"time":938000,"text":"To be able to change fences"},{"time":941000,"text":"and window guards into flowers,"},{"time":944000,"text":"it's fantastic."},{"time":946000,"text":"And here I've been working for the last three years"},{"time":949000,"text":"with a South Bronx developer"},{"time":951000,"text":"to bring art to life"},{"time":953000,"text":"to low-income buildings"},{"time":955000,"text":"and affordable housing."},{"time":958000,"text":"So each building has its own personality."},{"time":961000,"text":"And sometimes it's about a legacy of the neighborhood,"},{"time":965000,"text":"like in Morrisania, about the jazz history."},{"time":969000,"text":"And for other projects, like in Paris,"},{"time":972000,"text":"it's about the name of the street."},{"time":974000,"text":"It's called Rue des Prairies -- Prairie Street."},{"time":977000,"text":"So I brought back the rabbit,"},{"time":979000,"text":"the dragonfly,"},{"time":981000,"text":"to stay in that street."}]},{"cues":[{"time":983000,"text":"And in 2009,"},{"time":985000,"text":"I was asked to make a poster"},{"time":988000,"text":"to be placed in the subway cars in New York City"},{"time":991000,"text":"for a year."},{"time":993000,"text":"So that was a very captive audience."},{"time":997000,"text":"And I wanted to give them an escape."},{"time":1001000,"text":"I created \"All Around Town.\""},{"time":1004000,"text":"It is a papercutting,"},{"time":1006000,"text":"and then after, I added color on the computer."},{"time":1009000,"text":"So I can call it techno-crafted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1012000,"text":"And along the way,"},{"time":1014000,"text":"I'm kind of making papercuttings"},{"time":1017000,"text":"and adding other techniques."},{"time":1019000,"text":"But the result is always to have stories."},{"time":1022000,"text":"So the stories, they have a lot of possibilities."},{"time":1025000,"text":"They have a lot of scenarios."},{"time":1027000,"text":"I don't know the stories."},{"time":1029000,"text":"I take images from our global imagination,"},{"time":1033000,"text":"from cliché, from things we are thinking about,"},{"time":1035000,"text":"from history."},{"time":1037000,"text":"And everybody's a narrator,"},{"time":1039000,"text":"because everybody has a story to tell."},{"time":1042000,"text":"But more important"},{"time":1044000,"text":"is everybody has to make a story"},{"time":1046000,"text":"to make sense of the world."},{"time":1048000,"text":"And in all these universes,"},{"time":1050000,"text":"it's like imagination is the vehicle"},{"time":1053000,"text":"to be transported with,"},{"time":1055000,"text":"but the destination is our minds"},{"time":1058000,"text":"and how we can reconnect"},{"time":1060000,"text":"with the essential and with the magic."},{"time":1062000,"text":"And it's what story cutting is all about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1066000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}